{"tid":1292573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ WE CONNECT ] 國之概念文宣方向","createTime":"2019-07-07T11:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T11:25:43.000Z","uid":115847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"153b81d142facdcbd524d531978405c3092be758","tid":1292573,"uid":115847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T11:25:43.000Z","msg":"最近既文宣普遍都係針對條例同警察，<br />\n我認為可以開始對所有問題既源頭著手，<br />\n國 家 概 念。<br />\n<br />\n大部份未醒覺既人都係因為停留左係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港屬於中國</strong></span>既認知。<br />\n<br />\n而文宣方向可以強調得到清朝承認既<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">合法政權係<span style=\"color: blue;\">中華民國</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n並且放大<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中華人民共和國</span></span>統治下既&quot;<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">假</span></strong>&quot;，<br />\n假食物，假名牌，假新聞，假基建，<br />\n只因<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">上樑不正</span></strong>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>整個政權都係假</strong></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n務求令到一路以來既愛國人士感到被中共欺騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，加入抗共既行列。<br />\n<br />\n當大眾有左<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中華民國</span></span>先係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真中國</span></span>既共識，<br />\n下一步就係向國際宣告<span style=\"color: red;\">中華人民共和國</span>既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>不合法性</strong></span>。<br />\n繼而集合各國既力量對中共施加壓力，最終<del><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中華人民共和國</span></strong></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"}]}